fields.name: Bodhi Dog Bath Brush
fields.description:
Effective yet gentle bath brush. The soft rubber tips quickly scrub away dirt, dead skin and loose fur making it an excellent pet brush for grooming and bathing. It leaves pet skin clean and helps restore sheen and luster to the coat. Our handheld grooming tool wont pull on hair making it a perfect brush for pets with sensitive skin. Also increases the effectiveness of shampoo lathering, allowing less product to go further. Achieve a deeper clean than shampooing alone.

This dog bath brush can be used as deshedding tool to manage constant shedding. The split ends of the rubber teeth removes pet hair while not tugging excessively like other brushes do. The brush holds onto fur preventing it from flying around and making a mess. To remove hair from the brush, simply turn upside down and tap while gently pulling on the hair.

fields.name: Dispenser Bath Brush
fields.description:
The unique packaging design allows you to pour the shower gel into the brush to avoid waste and at the same time better clean your pets.The brush is made of high-quality soft silicone, no harmful substances, safe material and comfortable, very suitable for pet hair.

In addition to cleaning stains, the soft silicone tentacles can also massage the skin to improve blood circulation in dogs or cats. The brush adopts a special non-slip design to provide you with a comfortable grip when bathing your dog, and it can be easily hung after use.

**Can also be used for other pets, such as horses, rabbits, guinea pigs, etc.

fields.name: Bath Gloves
fields.description:
Hassle-free washing! Brush away your dogs or cats loose undercoat with ease. The fingers design of our deshedding grooming glove allows you to gently clean sensitive and hard-to-reach like the face, tail or legs. Instead of using the hard brush, use this glove while bathing your pet so you can clean your pet at the same time as you put on the pet shampoo.

Collects more hair & dirt- With 255 soft bristle Silicone tips, our pet hair remover glove gently traps more loose fur and shedding hair. Ideal for all coat types- long, short or curly. 

Easy care and clean up- As you brush your pet, shedding hair accumulates between the silicone tips and sticks to the glove. When youre done grooming, simply peel all hair out with 1 clean pull & you can continue washing your pet.

fields.name: Burt's Bees Shampoo & Conditioner Set
fields.description:
Join the millions of pet parents who cant get enough of Burts Bees for Pets by using Americas number one pet grooming brand. The perfect set for dogs with dry, itchy skin. This set includes one 16 ounce bottle of Burt's Bees for Pets Care Plus Hydrating Shampoo and and one 12 ounce bottle of Hydrating Conditioner. Made with coconut oil, which provides a natural infusion of moisture. Leaving coats silky and soft.

100% safe, veterinarian recommended formula, free of fragrances, sulfates, colorants, and harsh chemicals.

fields.name: Bed Cover
fields.description:
Protect your furniture from daily wear and tear, spills and stains. It's a great choice for homes with children and pets.100% Waterproof polyester. The compound waterproof layer in the fabric offers strength and durability with exceptional softness. Features thick layer of anti-slip backing with plastic drop printing, which attached the entire bed protector to prevent sliding. Machine washable. Wash warm, mild laundry detergent advised. Do not bleach.

Sizing:
Small- 52x82in
Medium- 68x82in
Large- 86x82in

fields.name: Collar & Leash Set
fields.description:
Tactical dog leash and collar set made by 1680D high-end durable nylon material with neat stitching and soft padded lining to prevent chafing for your dog's skin and hair with a comfortable fit. The service retractable dog leash has two handles, one handle at the end and one soft padded handle near the clip. The one close to the clip or collar area is nice to get control quickly on busy sidewalks, bike lanes, and crowded areas. Use the top handle when walking, running, or jogging, perfect for large and medium dogs.

Sizing:
Small- 12 inch
Med- 15 inch
Large- 20 inch

fields.name: Detangling Brush
fields.description: 2-in-1 Detangler. The double-sided detangler is an excellent two in one tool for your pets. Detangler gives your pet well-groomed, tangle-free coat, as the detangler brush has two sides. The coarse side is ideal for freeing up entangled hair and the finer side is suitable for combing out loose hair. Has ultra-soft intelliflex bristles, with intelligent flexibility- flexible on one stroke and firm on the next. The adaptive flexibility of intelliflex eliminates all tugging, tearing, pulling and ripping, providing ouch less brushing and detangling! Gentle and comfortable for dogs .

fields.name: Puppy Essentials- Group Class
fields.description:
Puppy training helps your puppy to get off to the right start.

This program will teach your dog how training works (its not innate!), basic cues for everyday life, and provide an introduction to leash walking behaviors. Plus, puppies will be exposed to other people, environments, and dogs, which improves sociability and reduces reactivity. 

Our trainers mold and shape dogs behavior using positive reinforcement and science-based methods. Positive reinforcement uses reward-based techniques and establishes long term positive associations.

- 10 Training Sessions
- 3 Weeks
- Six puppies per class

fields.name: Full Day Play
fields.description:
A full day of supervised playtime with other dogs of similar sizes and energy levels.

Guests in our All Day Play program get to romp around in spacious play areas with dogs of similar sizes and temperaments. This socialization-centric program helps pups build tolerance of environmental stimuli and hone their dog-to-dog communication skills.

fields.name: Puppy Essentials + Day Care
fields.description:
Puppy Essentials training with Day Care on training days. Drop off in the morning, pick up in the afternoon. 

Puppy Essentials:
This program will teach your dog how training works (its not innate!), basic cues for everyday life, and provide an introduction to leash walking behaviors. Plus, puppies will be exposed to other people, environments, and dogs, which improves sociability and reduces reactivity. 

Full Day Play:
A full day of supervised playtime with other dogs of similar sizes and energy levels.

Guests in our Full Day Play program get to romp around in spacious play areas with dogs of similar sizes and temperaments. This socialization-centric program helps pups build tolerance of environmental stimuli and hone their dog-to-dog communication skills.

- 10 Training sessions and full days of day care

fields.name: Valentines Day Special
fields.description:
Full Day Stay + Bath

Your pup enjoys a Full Day of Play with his fellow pups and gets a relaxing wash and dry before pick up time. Top off the day with a special Valentine's Day doggie cookie. The perfect V-Day gift!
